Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.98,0:00:09.40,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}57.3 db-FM!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.38,0:00:13.68,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Summer, summer, summer!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.68,0:00:17.14,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The heat on Donburi Island just won't let up.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.14,0:00:20.91,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's temperature has\Nfinally topped 45 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.91,0:00:23.38,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow, it really got that hot, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.38,0:00:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave-ho, heave-ho, heave-ho...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.31,0:00:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a little worm!  {earthworm-san}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:32.07,0:00:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What, a worm?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.59,0:00:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't stop working every time you find something, \NZakoBee! The boss'll chew you out.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.19,0:00:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But even a tiny 3.03 cm bug's got\Na tiny 1.5 cm soul. I can't just do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.19,0:00:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that every time you see a bug.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.54,0:00:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There, go away, little one.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.83,0:00:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you leave it out in this sun, it'll dry up.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.15,0:00:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really? {waru - his stock phrase, meaning "bad/evil"}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:57.18,0:00:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, go.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.38,0:01:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's dangerous around here.\NBetter run elsewhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.04,0:01:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.00,0:01:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.75,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.51,0:01:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Even for summer, it's extra hot today. {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.43,0:01:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It rained a little yesterday, \Nso now it's humid too—it feels like a sauna!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.15,0:01:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew... if I run out of this ice cream, \NI might actually die.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.92,0:01:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I will.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.18,0:01:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:30.68,0:01:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Roadwork in this heat?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.24,0:01:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel, why don't you try working part-time?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.21,0:01:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Might help you lose weight. {ii diet?}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:39.30,0:01:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's that supposed to mean, Madoka?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.75,0:01:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{waru}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.68,0:01:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, another worm?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.57,0:01:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.93,0:01:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dr. Warumon, \Nwhat are you doing? Working here?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.44,0:01:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're working hard, huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:01.31,0:02:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.38,0:02:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Dr. Warumon, that must\Nbe rough for you in this heat.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.53,0:02:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't strain your back too much.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.65,0:02:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give me those condescending looks!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.85,0:02:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't strain my back too much, you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.47,0:02:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare me your elderly sympathy! {lit: don't show me that kind of appreciation for the old age}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.16,0:02:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, kids!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.61,0:02:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as I get proper funding, \NI'll crush you with my ultimate mech!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.52,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You better be damn ready \Nfor the whooping of a lifetime!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.88,0:02:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No slacking off, you part-timer! {baito = part-timer}{Would it be too literal if "boy" was switched with "part-timer"? The latter sounds more natural and "boy" doesn't seem like it fits anyways since the boss clearly looks younger than Warumon -Marty}{ye w/e}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.49,0:02:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep that up and I'll dock your pay!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.92,0:02:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.68,0:02:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Please forgive me! \NI'll work seriously! I will!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.45,0:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it! Please cut me\Nsome slack! Right, here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.63,0:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We should head out. \NLet's not bother them.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.63,0:02:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.80,0:02:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.51,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.03,0:02:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee. {-chan}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.20,0:02:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.09,0:03:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Warumon's got it rough too.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.82,0:03:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Hey, Pastel, let's keep this\Na secret from Dr. Cinnamon, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.75,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Obviously.\NNo way we can tell him about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.52,0:04:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Uh, morning... it's morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.52,0:04:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.24,0:04:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up, your alarm clock rang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.89,0:04:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Bee?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.56,0:04:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee, why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.94,0:04:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand it myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.55,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? So you're not here to attack the lab\Nor anything Dr. Warumon told you to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then it's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.46,0:05:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm going jogging now. \NWanna come along, Bee?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'll run!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.92,0:05:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.05,0:05:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... You go on ahead, Bee.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.43,0:05:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.01,0:05:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!{fight}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.04,0:05:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.79,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.52,0:05:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Bee! Isn't it pretty?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.03,0:05:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's gonna be another hot day. \NLet's head back. Gotta make breakfast.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Affirmative!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:48.04,0:05:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run back to the lab. Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.59,0:05:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.22,0:06:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.38,0:06:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.31,0:06:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.81,0:06:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wake up! Geez...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Light!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.03,0:06:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{mou?}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.50,0:06:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he {\i1}will{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}wake up!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.37,0:06:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good mor—
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.30,0:06:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:26.83,0:06:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally got up.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.53,0:06:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning, it's the same old story...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.37,0:06:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? ZakoBee? Why's he here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.23,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Dr. Warumon's \Nplotting something again?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.25,0:06:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, that doesn't seem to be the case.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.85,0:06:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then why's he here?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's already sitting at the table \Nlike he belongs here...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.87,0:06:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Light. If he came to visit, \Nwe should treat him like a guest.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.53,0:06:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, meals are more fun \Nwith more people, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.22,0:06:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.03,0:07:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.12,0:07:03.63,Thought,,0,0,0,,Pastel... {maybe it's not thought?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.57,0:07:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, everyone, let's eat.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.03,0:07:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! I've been waiting!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.04,0:07:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.80,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.17,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? What's wrong, Bee? \NIt doesn't suit your taste?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.75,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Bee, what is it? Did you get\Na stomachache or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.11,0:07:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that hit the spot. {I'm full}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the meal.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.77,0:07:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.09,0:07:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you enjoyed it. \NDid everyone have enough?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.67,0:07:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm stifled! {he says "my chest is full" for some reason instead of "stomach"}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.40,0:07:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stifled? You probably meant to say "stuffed." {lit: chest? you meant belly, right?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.82,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap, Pastel! \NWe're gonna miss the crab train!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, we gotta go!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.12,0:07:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the cleanup to WinBee. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.52,0:07:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, Doc! Lunch is in the fridge—just heat it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.81,0:07:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.24,0:08:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait! L-Light!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Hold up, hold up!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.77,0:08:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, made it!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.58,0:08:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.83,0:08:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Morning, Light, Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, White! {i assume that's what he says and that's who this character is, because there's one listed on wiki: white\NVoice - Junichi Ichi\NHe is the class president of the class that Light and his friends attend. He has a crush on Pastel. Initially, he did not have a name, but one was given to him in "Dessert Middle School Ghost Stories Part 2," and this fact is often used as a topic of conversation.}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.04,0:08:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why's ZakoBee with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.53,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Bee, why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.58,0:08:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just follow us without knowing why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.72,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee, we're going to school now. \NWe can't play with you. Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.34,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.00,0:08:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! I wanna go too! \NI wanna see the school!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.35,0:08:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.92,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold up, Bee...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.38,0:08:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee is gonna behave! \NHe's gonna be the humblest child ever!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.42,0:09:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, today we'll continue{ what we started last week} \Nfrom page 89 of the textbook.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.04,0:09:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, impressive!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.23,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel's notebook is filled to the brim!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.80,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.71,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"What should I make for dinner tonight? \NOh, I know—Pom! {?????? そーだ！ぽむ! - no idea what this pomu could mean, it doesn't make any sense at all here; it appears to me that this and the next line are about some made up dish}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it «Mer Chetille!» Oh, that's lovely. {sounds like a mock of french}{ 『メル・チェティーリェ』に決定\Nキメキメ~\Nあ〜でも前に作った時、お兄ちゃんにもっとお肉はトロ~リ\Nけるく}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.86,0:09:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... But last time I made it, Light complained the\Nmeat wasn't simmered enough to melt in your mouth. {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.12,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, cut me some slack! \NI'm not a full-time housewife, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who has that kind of time, idiot?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.28,0:09:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, now I'm annoyed.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.14,0:09:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! Tomorrow, I'll only fry \Nthe almost-expired eggs for him especially."
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.56,0:09:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.95,0:10:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"Whoa, that was close! \NThe teacher almost caught me." {he's still reading the notes; lit: accidentally made eye contact with sensei - probably means she attracted attention or was almost called to the blackboard}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.40,0:10:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear me, Pastel, \NI think your notes are a little off-topic.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.07,0:10:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're sweating a lot. \NWhat's wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.17,0:10:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Sweating? \NIs it because of the heat?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.35,0:10:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Teacher, let's go to the pool! \NLet's make it a swimming class!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's good...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.23,0:10:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.01,0:10:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I suddenly change today's plans \Nand make it a swimming lesson?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How weird...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.16,0:10:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.54,0:10:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,On a hot day like this, \Nthe pool really is the best.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the pool's the best.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.37,0:10:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got Bee to thank for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.66,0:10:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.80,0:10:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right! It's so hot, \Nthere's no way I could focus in class.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.62,0:10:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like we've been saved.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.59,0:10:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, this really helped.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.68,0:10:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.22,0:10:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you, kid? {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.51,0:11:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Name's ZakoBee.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.01,0:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? ZakoBee, huh? {-chan}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.06,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you girls! \NThis is still class time, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice your swimming properly.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.96,0:11:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.44,0:11:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially you, Madoka. \NYou need to work on being able to float. {meaning she can't swim at all yet}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.68,0:11:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you can't swim?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.64,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I'm kind of scared of the water.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you swim, Bee?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.51,0:11:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that looks fun! Me next!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,This is great! It's so bouncy! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee, you're amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.18,0:11:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry, my back feels so warm...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, he sank!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.18,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All righty! Time to head home.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So how did you like school?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.22,0:11:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was great fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.38,0:12:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Feels like we ended up just playing around most of the day.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.38,0:12:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.92,0:12:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.75,0:12:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... isn't this the construction site \Nwhere Bee was working yesterday?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's tough work.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.34,0:12:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't earn money\Nwithout breaking a sweat.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.38,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{H-Huh?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.88,0:12:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{Hm?}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{Oh!}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.21,0:12:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! ZakoBee! You little...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the heck have you been all this time?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.75,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been looking all over! \NSkipping work like that...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.06,0:12:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Master! Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.07,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I forgive you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.65,0:12:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.68,0:12:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, Master...\NIs there some kind of catch?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:44.60,0:12:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way you'd forgive me that easily...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.29,0:12:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.52,0:12:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly, you fool!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.36,0:12:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pretend to be a kind master at first,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.90,0:13:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,then once we're back at the lab, I'll subject you to horrors beyond human comprehension! {lit: I'll do that and this and maybe even that}{memesubs, fix this. -marty}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.09,0:13:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry! Please forgive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I forgive you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew, that's a relief.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.31,0:13:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey... doesn't something feel off today?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be that maybe... maybe...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.80,0:13:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna meet the Cookie God!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.28,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you! You're the Cookie God?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.67,0:13:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Cookie!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.17,0:13:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really are the Cookie God! \NI'm so happy to finally meet you!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.46,0:13:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Madoka, is that thing really...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.93,0:13:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is {\i1}that{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}the way you address a god, Pastel?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.84,0:13:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, sorry. So is this dignified entity \Nthe “Cookie God” Madoka always talks about? {sono okata = very respectful}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.78,0:14:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I'm so moved to finally meet him!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.17,0:14:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing! \NI had only to say it out loud, and it came true!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.89,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Cookie!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.87,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish all today's homework would disappear!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.71,0:14:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I changed my mind! \NNever mind the homework I gave you today.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.39,0:14:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.57,0:14:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, and please pass that along \Nin the phone chain, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.04,0:14:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.77,0:14:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I want a McDorian tropical shake, large!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.27,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! {yari?}{does she say anything here?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, me too!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.82,0:14:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you lot!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.82,0:14:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you messing with me again?! {by summoning cold drinks for themselves}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.01,0:14:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sweating buckets out here \Nworking in this scorching heat,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.14,0:14:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're just goofing off, sipping drinks?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! You want one, Dr. Warumon?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.33,0:14:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch! Who'd ever want that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.89,0:14:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.46,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee, you want one?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.34,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not “yeah,” get back to work!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.47,0:15:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Cookie!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.18,0:15:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, Light...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.37,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what on Earth is going on.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:13.29,0:15:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe our hidden superpowers \Nawakened or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.03,0:15:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the will of the universe \Nchose us to protect Earth? {is this a fucking ambassador magma reference}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.45,0:15:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is the start \Nof some huge psycho adventure!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.70,0:15:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably someone's dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:27.28,0:15:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.52,0:15:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a dream... That makes sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.58,0:15:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Kids these days...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.61,0:15:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying even this exhaustion\Nand grime on my hands is a dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.02,0:15:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And does it hurt when I pinch? {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.71,0:15:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My face hurts! It can't stretch that much! {??????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.15,0:15:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That just means\Nit's a super realistic dream, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.51,0:15:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, if it's a dream, \Nthen I only need to make a wish,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.73,0:15:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and I could become an idol whose popularity
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.25,0:16:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is not limited to only Donburi, \Nbut spreads across the whole galaxy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.13,0:16:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph. Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.46,0:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.64,0:16:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is it really a dream? \NDo dreams really let you do anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.93,0:16:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, let's say, if I wished for a ton of money...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.51,0:16:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,then, inside this wallet that usually\Nmakes me sigh every time I open it...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.05,0:16:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:31.18,0:16:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.29,0:16:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A-And then...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.27,0:16:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,since it's a dream, even if I empty it, \Nwhen I open it again...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.54,0:16:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! More money every time I open it!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.84,0:16:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.07,0:16:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, with this much money, \Nyou won't have to work anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.45,0:16:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can build anti-TwinBee mechas \Nas much as you want!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.70,0:16:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... you're still an idiot. \NThis is a dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.46,0:17:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Appear! The ultimate robot!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.31,0:17:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not done yet!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.52,0:17:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Appear! An even bigger ultimate robot!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.90,0:17:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! N-Not one, but {\i1}two{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}brand new ultimate mechas?! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.20,0:17:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No budget limits at all! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.58,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only warming up! {lit: approaching ultimate excitement }
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.34,0:17:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can crush the TwinBee team! Easy win! {????}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid? {???? maybe "why deal with them one by one"}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.74,0:17:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about TwinBee? \NWho cares about Cinnamon? Too much work!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just buy up the planet wholesale! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.61,0:17:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.30,0:17:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Success!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, my turn!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.49,0:17:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna be super popular with tons of cute girls!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.17,0:17:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.77,0:18:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it... I knew something was missing.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.24,0:18:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then suddenly,\Na shy, sickly girl also appears! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.92,0:18:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.34,0:18:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... I'm kind of frail. {have weak health}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.53,0:18:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, as long as you stay cheerful!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{kugumo?? idk, maybe just frustration SFX, like "ugh..."}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You jerk! {??????? dunno why she's mad either}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.41,0:18:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{cookie}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.60,0:18:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka's special cookies, \Nfresh out of the oven!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, don't push!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.05,0:18:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Cookies... {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.05,0:18:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,With sea cucumber, with cabbage{/kale}, \Nwith fermented fish{kusaya; brined, sun-dried fish (usu. mackerel scad) which has a very pungent smell}, all loaded with vinegar!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:41.40,0:18:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,More... Give me more!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.66,0:18:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do I always end up coming back for more?! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.05,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.77,0:18:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee, they look like zombies.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.99,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,WinBee, let's make a wish too!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.55,0:18:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your wish going to bee?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.39,0:18:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.08,0:19:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna be an idol like Pastel!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:04.84,0:19:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wink... {?? sparkling sfx}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.71,0:19:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanna go to Soltias, \Nback to where I was born!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Make some noise! {???? mb "did you like it"}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.64,0:19:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Bee? \NDon't you have anything you want?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.62,0:19:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... Bee is happy\Njust being with you, Pastel.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.78,0:19:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're so sweet!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.11,0:19:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Bee is happy...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.87,0:19:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But still, even if this is a dream, \Nwhose dream is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.88,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.50,0:19:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on, does it really matter?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.98,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, yeah. At times like this, \Nwe usually ask Mint. But where is he?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.26,0:20:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, he says the key point is that\Neven though any wish can come true,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.88,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing has strayed too far from everyday life.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.22,0:20:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So that means there's\Nprobably someone who's satisfied
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.89,0:20:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,with things as they are, \Nwithout making any big wishes.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.13,0:20:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That person is likely the one dreaming all this.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.04,0:20:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I shouldn't translate the next part...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.14,0:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, I see. As expected of Mint.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.75,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No problem, that was easy, he says.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.39,0:20:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But that also means that Mint \Nis probably going to scold me again later...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.03,0:20:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.92,0:21:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, who could it be...? I mean, all those\Nbeauties are nice, but... uh, what am I saying? {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.64,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here for you! {???? iru yo? I have no idea what he said in prev line}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.88,0:21:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Light! Don't embarrass us like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.06,0:21:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So, someone who's satisfied \Nwithout making any special wishes...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.76,0:21:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, who could it be?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.22,0:21:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.98,0:21:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was {\i1}my{\i0}{\i0\fsp3} {\fsp0}dream?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.81,0:21:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Why did this have to happen?! \NSuch a nice dream got ruined!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.05,0:21:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you so early in the morning?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.22,0:21:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is it already time to get up?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.58,0:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, ZakoBee, \Nwash your face and get to work already.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.22,0:21:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, nice weather today.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:59.22,0:22:00.85,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clear skies again today.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:00.85,0:22:04.47,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The high is expected to exceed 45 degrees again. {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.47,0:22:08.06,Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wow, over 45 again? That's just brutal.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.27,0:22:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, at least it was a fun dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:11.72,0:22:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, ZakoBee! Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.60,0:22:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye-aye!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.83,0:22:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's topic: "My Dream." \NFeaturing:
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.22,0:22:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,TwinBee—Mayumi "At my age,\NI don't really have big dreams anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.39,0:22:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to pass away peacefully... but if anything,\NI'd like to outlive Yukimasa Kishino first." Tanaka. {kishino yukimasa is the voice of warumon, fans were shortening his name as a joke to K野Y正 = K[ishi]no Y(read as "wai")[ki]masa - together it gives us "keino waimasa"}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.52,0:22:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Pastel—Hekiru "Um... I'd like to be reborn as a guy\Nand go on a training journey around the world." Shina.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.32,0:22:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,WinBee and Teacher Apple—Kumiko\N"I want to get rich and live in Hawaii!" Nishihara.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:52.21,0:23:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Mint, GwinBee, and Cute Girl C—Miki\N"If I were reborn, I'd want to be a long-lasting idol." Ito.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.11,0:23:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Cinnamon—Kazumi "Check out all\Nthe hot springs in the country." Tanaka.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.10,0:23:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Madoka—Kokuda "I want Madoka's cookies\Nto actually turn out normal." Mariko.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.53,0:23:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,ZakoBee—Yusuke "I want to go\Nto space someday." Numata.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.18,0:23:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari—Natsumi "I get lonely easily, so I wish someone\Nwould always be there to be by my side." Yanase.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.01,0:23:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,White—Atsushi "In 30 years,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.82,0:23:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make a TwinBee Paradise Junior\Nwith the kids of the current cast." Kisaichi.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.15,0:23:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Construction Site Foreman—Koichi \N"I'd like to own a small shop someday." Nagano.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.34,0:23:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Woman A, Sickly Girl—Asako \N"I seriously wanna be a cute girl." Shirakura.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:37.83,0:23:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Warumon—Yukimasa "If I'm reborn,\NI wanna be an idol." Kishino.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.67,0:23:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Light—Kappei "Family safety \Nand protection from bad luck." Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:47.03,0:23:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That concludes our program!
Comment: 0,0:23:49.75,0:23:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,
